title: Tech View: Nifty50 chart suggests weakness; support seen at 17,700 level - Economic Times
content: Tech View: Nifty50 chart suggests weakness; support seen at 17,700 level  Economic Times
description: Wednesday's pattern confirms a short-term top reversal at the swing high of 18,114 level and a beginning of a downward correction in the market, said Nagaraj Shetti of HDFC Securities.
